-- CNO’s Bonach Says Buybacks a Priority as Shares ‘Screaming Buy’
-- B y   Z a c h a r y   T r a c e r
-- 2012-06-13T20:39:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-13/cno-s-bonach-says-buybacks-a-priority-as-shares-screaming-buy-.html
CNO Financial Group Inc. (CNO)  Chief
Executive Officer Edward Bonach said share buybacks are a
priority for the insurer.  “We’re still trading at roughly half of book,” Bonach
said today at an investor conference in New York. “We think
it’s a screaming buy from the standpoint of our capital
deployment.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
